Run your Main.java (no changes needed).

Then, in Bank.java, you can call methods like:

Bank bank = new Bank(connection);
bank.addCustomer(new Customer(1, "John Doe", "john@example.com"));
bank.getAllCustomers().forEach(System.out::println);
bank.deleteCustomer(1);



